[ CELL PHONE RINGING ]
[ SCREAMS ]

215
00:12:25,404 --> 00:12:27,771
UH, HELLO?
OKUMURA HERE.

216
00:12:27,804 --> 00:12:30,004
<i>- [ SHIEMI ]</i>
<i>RIN.</i>
- SHIEMI?

217
00:12:30,038 --> 00:12:33,104
- HEY, WHAT'S UP?
- I NEED YOUR HELP
WITH SOMETHING.

218
00:12:34,538 --> 00:12:36,538
YES. AND HURRY.

219
00:12:36,571 --> 00:12:38,304
GOTCHA.
I'M ON THE WAY.

220
00:12:57,383 --> 00:12:58,783
[ GROANS ]

221
00:13:02,050 --> 00:13:03,250
[ GASPING ]

222
00:13:03,283 --> 00:13:04,983
[ SQUEAKING ]

223
00:13:07,383 --> 00:13:10,150
WHAT'S THIS?

224
00:13:14,017 --> 00:13:16,250
[ SHIEMI ]
YOU'RE AWAKE.
THANK GOODNESS.

225
00:13:16,283 --> 00:13:20,183
- HUH?
- TRY NOT TO OVEREXERT
YOURSELF, OKAY?

226
00:13:20,217 --> 00:13:23,417
WHERE AM I?
HOW DID I GET HERE?

227
00:13:23,450 --> 00:13:26,650
- I DON'T REMEMBER.
- I FOUND YOU IN MY GARDEN.

228
00:13:26,683 --> 00:13:28,150
YOU WERE UNCONSCIOUS.

229
00:13:28,183 --> 00:13:31,050
I COULDN'T CARRY YOU,
BUT IT WASN'T A PROBLEM FOR HIM.

230
00:13:31,083 --> 00:13:33,750
NEE!

231
00:13:33,783 --> 00:13:36,217
I'M SORRY, BUT I DON'T KNOW
WHO YOU ARE.

232
00:13:36,250 --> 00:13:38,083
OH, NOBODY SPECIAL.

233
00:13:38,117 --> 00:13:41,083
JUST AN EXORCIST
IN TRAINING, IS ALL.

234
00:13:41,117 --> 00:13:43,250
AN EXORCIST.

235
00:13:44,617 --> 00:13:47,283
HELLO? ANYBODY HO--

236
00:13:47,317 --> 00:13:49,050
NOPE.
NO ONE'S HOME.

237
00:13:49,083 --> 00:13:51,250
AND AFTER COMING
ALL THE WAY OUT HERE.

238
00:13:51,283 --> 00:13:52,650
NEE-EE!

239
00:13:52,683 --> 00:13:56,217
OH. HEY, WHAT UP?
IS SHIEMI AROUND?

240
00:13:56,250 --> 00:13:58,417
NEE! NEE, NEE!

241
00:13:58,450 --> 00:14:00,017
OH, LEAD THE WAY THEN.

242
00:14:00,050 --> 00:14:02,717
NEE, NEE! NEE, NEE!
NEE, NEE!

243
00:14:02,750 --> 00:14:04,450
HEY, SHIEMI!

244
00:14:04,483 --> 00:14:06,850
WHAT THE--
NEE, NEE-EE.

245
00:14:06,883 --> 00:14:09,250
I DON'T REMEMBER SEEING
THESE STEPS BEFORE.

246
00:14:09,283 --> 00:14:11,283
[ GASPS ]

247
00:14:11,317 --> 00:14:13,250
WHAT'S GOING ON?

248
00:14:13,283 --> 00:14:15,583
SHURA'S FAMILIAR?

249
00:14:15,617 --> 00:14:18,283
NO WAY.
THAT MEANS SHE'S HERE.

250
00:14:19,683 --> 00:14:22,150
THIS WAS MY GRANDMA'S
SECRET GARDEN.

251
00:14:22,183 --> 00:14:24,117
SHE LEFT IT TO ME
TO TAKE CARE OF.

252
00:14:24,150 --> 00:14:27,550
- OH.
- MY GRANDMA USED
TO ALWAYS TELL ME...

253
00:14:27,583 --> 00:14:30,683
THAT IF I JUST STOPPED
AND LISTENED TO WHAT THE PLANTS
WERE SAYING,

254
00:14:30,717 --> 00:14:32,783
THEY'D BE SURE TO BLOSSOM.

255
00:14:32,817 --> 00:14:34,917
AND YOU KNOW?
SHE WAS RIGHT.

256
00:14:34,950 --> 00:14:39,150
LOOK AROUND.
THERE'S NO DOUBT
GRANDMA COULD HEAR THEIR VOICES.

257
00:14:39,183 --> 00:14:43,083
IT'S AMAZING TO THINK
HOW MUCH ALL THE FAIRIES
IN THE GARDEN LOVED HER.

258
00:14:43,117 --> 00:14:46,917
BUT THEN MY GRANDMA
WAS AN AMAZING PERSON.

259
00:14:46,950 --> 00:14:52,117
OH! I'M SORRY.
I DIDN'T MEAN
TO GO ON AND ON LIKE THAT.

260
00:14:52,150 --> 00:14:55,217
I GUESS THIS IS WHAT
THE GARDEN OF AMAHARA
WOULD BE LIKE.

261
00:14:55,250 --> 00:14:56,650
HUH?

262
00:14:56,683 --> 00:14:59,117
MY HUSBAND TOLD ME
ABOUT IT ONCE.

263
00:14:59,150 --> 00:15:01,417
HE SAID IT'S A PLACE
GOD MADE...

264
00:15:01,450 --> 00:15:04,283
WHERE ALL THE PLANTS
IN THE WORLD
HAD BEEN GATHERED.

265
00:15:04,317 --> 00:15:07,083
IF THERE REALLY IS
A GARDEN LIKE THAT,

266
00:15:07,117 --> 00:15:09,217
I'M SURE IT WOULD BE
A LOT LIKE HERE.

267
00:15:09,250 --> 00:15:11,883
UM, IF YOU WANT,
COULD WE BE FRIENDS?

268
00:15:11,917 --> 00:15:14,183
BESIDES GRANDMA,
YOU'RE THE ONLY ONE
I'VE MET...

269
00:15:14,217 --> 00:15:16,483
WHO KNOWS ABOUT
THE GARDEN OF AMAHARA.

270
00:15:16,517 --> 00:15:19,950
MM. YOUR HANDS ARE SO WARM.

271
00:15:19,983 --> 00:15:21,750
UM, WHAT'S YOUR NAME?

272
00:15:21,783 --> 00:15:24,850
MY NAME?
MY NAME IS
SHIEMI MORIYAMA.

273
00:15:24,883 --> 00:15:28,350
- I'M MICHELLE.
- SHIEMI.

274
00:15:28,383 --> 00:15:29,783
- [ GASPS ]
- RIN?

275
00:15:29,817 --> 00:15:32,317
GET AWAY FROM HER RIGHT NOW!

276
00:15:32,350 --> 00:15:33,717
[ GASPING ]
STAY BACK!

277
00:15:33,750 --> 00:15:37,350
- LET HER GO!
- SO YOU'RE WITH SATAN TOO.

278
00:15:37,383 --> 00:15:38,950
I SHOULD'VE GUESSED.
HUH?

279
00:15:38,983 --> 00:15:41,550
SHIEMI'S GOT NOTHING
TO DO WITH THIS.

280
00:15:41,583 --> 00:15:43,883
I WILL HAVE MY REVENGE.

281
00:15:43,917 --> 00:15:47,550
EVERYTHING I EVER LOVED
WAS BURNED TO ASHES.

282
00:15:47,583 --> 00:15:50,117
BLUE FLAMES
BURNED IT ALL AWAY!

283
00:15:53,583 --> 00:15:55,717
I WON'T FORGIVE SATAN FOR THAT.

284
00:15:55,750 --> 00:15:58,150
HE TOOK EVERYTHING I LOVED
AWAY FROM ME,

285
00:15:58,183 --> 00:16:00,517
AND TO MAKE HIM PAY,
I'M GOING TO--

286
00:16:00,550 --> 00:16:03,317
I'LL TAKE... EVERYTHING
AWAY FROM YOU.

287
00:16:03,350 --> 00:16:05,183
I SWEAR.

288
00:16:05,217 --> 00:16:06,650
[ GASPS ]

289
00:16:06,683 --> 00:16:09,350
- SHIEMI!
- MICHELLE?

290
00:16:09,383 --> 00:16:11,150
[ GRUNTS ]
NO, WAIT!

291
00:16:11,183 --> 00:16:16,383
SHE'S HURT REALLY BAD.
I'VE GOT TO TAKE CARE OF HER.

292
00:16:16,417 --> 00:16:18,317
YOU CAN'T HELP HER.

293
00:16:18,350 --> 00:16:21,083
SHE'S ALREADY DEAD.
WHAT?

294
00:16:21,117 --> 00:16:25,783
SHE'S A CORPSE
THAT WAS BROUGHT BACK TO LIFE
TO GET REVENGE ON SATAN.

295
00:16:25,817 --> 00:16:27,817
SO GET BACK, SHIEMI.

296
00:16:27,850 --> 00:16:30,617
YOU CAN'T.
MICHELLE'S NOT EVIL.
I KNOW IT.

297
00:16:30,650 --> 00:16:34,750
SHE TRIED TO KILL SUGURO,
THE GUYS AND EVERYONE
AT THE MONASTERY.

298
00:16:34,783 --> 00:16:37,883
NONE OF MY FRIENDS ARE SAFE
AS LONG AS SHE'S AROUND.

299
00:16:37,917 --> 00:16:40,083
I DIDN'T CALL YOU
BECAUSE I WAS IN DANGER.

300
00:16:40,117 --> 00:16:41,850
I CALLED YOU BECAUSE
I NEEDED YOUR HELP.

301
00:16:41,883 --> 00:16:44,650
AND THAT'S WHY I'M HERE--
TO HELP YOU.

302
00:16:44,683 --> 00:16:46,250
I'LL PROTECT YOU
FROM THAT THING.

303
00:16:46,283 --> 00:16:47,483
NO!

304
00:16:47,517 --> 00:16:49,917
I NEVER ASKED YOU TO DO THAT!

305
00:16:49,950 --> 00:16:52,483
SHIEMI.
LOOK AT HER.

306
00:16:53,683 --> 00:16:54,783
IF SHE'S EVIL,
NEE AND THE OTHERS...

307
00:16:54,817 --> 00:16:57,383
WOULDN'T HAVE TAKEN TO HER
LIKE THAT.

308
00:16:57,417 --> 00:16:59,850
[ FAIRIES ]
NEE!
YOU SEE?

309
00:17:03,683 --> 00:17:05,083
[ SIGHS ]

310
00:17:07,783 --> 00:17:11,150
BY THE WAY, SHE'S
MR. NOIHAUS'S WIFE.

311
00:17:11,183 --> 00:17:12,283
WHAT?

312
00:17:12,317 --> 00:17:14,150
<i>[ BUSY TONE ]</i>
[ RIN ]
CAN'T GET A SIGNAL HERE.

313
00:17:14,183 --> 00:17:16,583
I GOTTA MAKE A CALL.

314
00:17:16,617 --> 00:17:19,017
I'LL BE BACK IN A SEC.
OKAY.

315
00:17:19,050 --> 00:17:23,050
[ RIN ] HELLO?
[ SHURA ]
HEY, RIN. WHAT'S UP?

316
00:17:23,083 --> 00:17:26,383
I FOUND HER.
<i>YOU DID? SERIOUSLY?</i>

317
00:17:26,417 --> 00:17:28,717
<i>WHERE IS SHE?</i>
THE SUPPLY SHOP.

318
00:17:28,750 --> 00:17:30,583
WHAT THE HELL
IS SHE DOING THERE?

319
00:17:30,617 --> 00:17:32,750
HOW SHOULD I KNOW?
I JUST GOT HERE.

320
00:17:32,783 --> 00:17:34,683
I'M COMING OVER
AND BRINGING NOIHAUS.

321
00:17:34,717 --> 00:17:36,850
DON'T LET HER OUT
OF YOUR SIGHT.
YOU GOT THAT?

322
00:17:36,883 --> 00:17:40,617
ACTUALLY, DON'T COME OVER.
FOR REAL. DON'T.
<i>HUH?</i>

323
00:17:40,650 --> 00:17:42,317
WHAT'S THE MATTER, RIN?

324
00:17:42,350 --> 00:17:45,050
<i>SOMETHING GOING ON?</i>
<i>HEY--</i>
[ BEEPS ]

325
00:17:45,083 --> 00:17:47,383
[ ANGEL ]
WHAT A MAGNIFICENT GARDEN.

326
00:17:47,417 --> 00:17:53,250
IT'S REALLY BEAUTIFUL.
DEFINITELY NOT A PLACE
FOR DEMONS.

327
00:17:53,283 --> 00:17:54,717
[ RUMBLING ]

328
00:17:54,750 --> 00:17:56,983
[ GUNS COCKING ]
[ GASPS ]

329
00:18:01,017 --> 00:18:04,550
[ MAN ]
SIR AUGUSTE,
WE'VE CAPTURED THE SUSPECT.

330
00:18:04,583 --> 00:18:05,783
RIN!

331
00:18:05,817 --> 00:18:08,350
SO YOU WERE HIDING HERE
THE WHOLE TIME,

332
00:18:08,383 --> 00:18:11,050
YOU DEMON IN HUMAN SKIN.

333
00:18:11,083 --> 00:18:12,150
[ GRUNTING ]

334
00:18:12,183 --> 00:18:14,917
THERE IS NO GREATER TABOO
THAN RESURRECTING THE DEAD.

335
00:18:14,950 --> 00:18:17,183
IT VIOLATES
THE LAWS OF ASSIAH.

336
00:18:17,217 --> 00:18:19,517
I CONDEMN YOU
IN THE NAME OF THE VATICAN.

337
00:18:19,550 --> 00:18:21,650
- MICHELLE!
- [ MUFFLED ]
STOP!

338
00:18:21,683 --> 00:18:23,217
HMM.

339
00:18:23,250 --> 00:18:24,983
[ SWORD RINGING ]

340
00:18:26,383 --> 00:18:28,017
OUT OF MY WAY!

341
00:18:28,050 --> 00:18:31,817
[ NOIHAUS ]
I WILL ATONE FOR ALL
OF MICHELLE'S CRIMES.

342
00:18:31,850 --> 00:18:34,383
PLEASE HAVE MERCY ON HER.

343
00:18:34,417 --> 00:18:36,683
LET MY WIFE GO.

344
00:18:36,717 --> 00:18:38,317
I BEG YOU.

345
00:18:38,350 --> 00:18:41,383
BRAVO TO YOU AND YOUR
MATRIMONIAL COMMITMENTS.

346
00:18:41,417 --> 00:18:43,383
- [ GRUNTS ]
- SPARE ME!

347
00:18:43,417 --> 00:18:46,183
THE DEAD SHALL ONLY BE
RESURRECTED AT THE RAPTURE...

348
00:18:46,217 --> 00:18:49,683
WHEN THE ANGELS
BLOW THEIR TRUMPETS
FOR THE LAST TIME!

349
00:18:49,717 --> 00:18:51,750
STOP IT!

350
00:18:54,617 --> 00:18:56,850
[ GROANS, GASPS ]

351
00:18:56,883 --> 00:19:00,317
DEFENDING DEMONS NOW,
SON OF SATAN?

352
00:19:00,350 --> 00:19:05,150
NO. I JUST THINK YOU GUYS SUCK
FOR BUSTING IN HERE
AND TEARING THE PLACE UP.

353
00:19:05,183 --> 00:19:10,217
