WHAT YOU SAY.

355
00:19:13,517 --> 00:19:15,483
- RIN!
- [ STEEL CLANGING ]

356
00:19:15,517 --> 00:19:17,083
[ THINKING ]
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

357
00:19:17,117 --> 00:19:20,550
THE SON OF SATAN
FIGHTING TO PROTECT US.

358
00:19:20,583 --> 00:19:24,983
AND AFTER I TRIED TO TAKE
EVERYTHING AWAY
THAT WAS DEAR TO HIM. WHY?

359
00:19:25,017 --> 00:19:27,383
IS THAT THE BEST YOU CAN DO,
SATAN'S SPAWN?

360
00:19:27,417 --> 00:19:30,317
YOU WANNA GO?
LET'S GO!

361
00:19:30,350 --> 00:19:33,050
[ SHOUTING ]

362
00:19:33,083 --> 00:19:34,350
SNAKE FANG!

363
00:19:34,383 --> 00:19:37,217
[ SHOUTING, GRUNTS ]

364
00:19:37,250 --> 00:19:39,817
WHAT THE HELL?
SHURA?

365
00:19:39,850 --> 00:19:42,617
WOULD YOU JUST CHILL?
YOU ARE NOT HELPING ANYONE.

366
00:19:42,650 --> 00:19:45,317
JUST GET OUT OF MY WAY.

367
00:19:45,350 --> 00:19:48,483
IS THIS WHAT YOU WANT?
REALLY?
COME ON, THINK.

368
00:19:48,517 --> 00:19:51,150
OUT OF MY WAY!

369
00:19:51,183 --> 00:19:53,917
[ GUNSHOT ]

370
00:19:56,217 --> 00:19:58,717
[ SCREAMS ]

371
00:19:58,750 --> 00:20:00,617
- MICHELLE!
- OH, NO.

372
00:20:00,650 --> 00:20:02,317
[ NOIHAUS GASPING ]

373
00:20:02,350 --> 00:20:04,450
STAY WITH ME, MICHELLE.

374
00:20:04,483 --> 00:20:06,550
MICHELLE!
DAMN IT!

375
00:20:06,583 --> 00:20:09,617
WHICH ONE OF YOU SHOT HER, HUH?

376
00:20:09,650 --> 00:20:11,783
WHICH ONE OF YOU COWARDS WAS IT?

377
00:20:11,817 --> 00:20:14,617
- STOP IT, RIN!
- COME ON!
I'LL TAKE ALL OF YOU--

378
00:20:14,650 --> 00:20:17,217
- THE GARDEN OF AMAHARA.
- STEP UP, YOU DA--

379
00:20:17,250 --> 00:20:22,117
THAT PARADISE
WHERE ALL THE PLANTS
IN THE WORLD ARE GATHERED.

380
00:20:23,683 --> 00:20:27,283
IT'S NOT HERE,
BUT I KNOW IT'S REAL.

381
00:20:27,317 --> 00:20:31,250
IF WE CAN JUST FIND IT,
I KNOW WE CAN LIVE IN PEACE.

382
00:20:31,283 --> 00:20:33,617
WE CAN FIND IT TOGETHER,

383
00:20:33,650 --> 00:20:35,283
JUST YOU AND ME.

384
00:20:35,317 --> 00:20:36,983
MY DARLING.

385
00:20:42,417 --> 00:20:44,650
[ ANGEL ]
DON'T JUST STAND THERE.

386
00:20:44,683 --> 00:20:46,817
ARREST THOSE HERETICS!
THAT'S AN ORDER!

387
00:20:46,850 --> 00:20:48,250
THAT'S ENOUGH!

388
00:20:49,183 --> 00:20:51,850
[ SHOUTING ]

389
00:20:51,883 --> 00:20:53,917
- [ GASPS ]
- [ ALL ]
NEE.

390
00:20:55,317 --> 00:20:58,683
I'VE NEVER SEEN SO MANY
BABY GREENMEN BEFORE.

391
00:20:58,717 --> 00:21:01,750
CURSES!
[ BELLS TOLLING ]

392
00:21:09,883 --> 00:21:12,217
[ MAN ]
SIR AUGUSTE.

393
00:21:12,250 --> 00:21:15,983
YES, I KNOW.
RETREAT.

394
00:21:16,017 --> 00:21:18,717
WHAT'S UP WITH
ALL THE BELLS?

395
00:21:18,750 --> 00:21:21,483
IT'S AN EMERGENCY SUMMONS
FROM THE VATICAN.

396
00:21:21,517 --> 00:21:23,717
THAT CAN'T BE A GOOD THING.

397
00:21:24,917 --> 00:21:27,783
HEY, YOU THINK IT'S GONNA
WORK OUT FOR THEM?

398
00:21:27,817 --> 00:21:31,917
I HOPE IT DOES.
IF ANYONE CAN FIND IT, THEY CAN.

399
00:21:31,950 --> 00:21:36,750
THE GARDEN OF AMAHARA,
A PLACE WHERE THEY CAN
LIVE IN PEACE.

400
00:21:46,750 --> 00:21:49,450
♪ [ WOMAN SINGING
IN JAPANESE ]

401
00:23:10,283 --> 00:23:12,817
ARTHUR AUGUSTE ANGEL
AT YOUR SERVICE, MILORD.

