PALADIN.

403
00:23:17,317 --> 00:23:19,417
WHERE ARE THE GRIGORI?

404
00:23:19,450 --> 00:23:22,150
I'VE RELIEVED THEM.
IMPOSSIBLE!

405
00:23:22,183 --> 00:23:25,517
THEY ARE THE SUPREME ADVISERS TO
THE KNIGHTS OF THE TRUE CROSS.

406
00:23:25,550 --> 00:23:27,850
THAT'S ALL IN THE PAST NOW.

407
00:23:27,883 --> 00:23:32,683
FROM THIS DAY FORWARD,
I, ERNST FREDERIK EGIN,

408
00:23:32,717 --> 00:23:35,283
WILL TAKE COMMAND OF
THE KNIGHTS OF THE TRUE CROSS.

409
00:23:36,517 --> 00:23:38,050
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING ]

410
00:23:40,750 --> 00:23:42,517
[ EGIN ]
GENTLEMEN, THROUGHOUT HISTORY,

411
00:23:42,550 --> 00:23:44,683
HUMANITY HAS BEEN
ON THE DEFENSIVE.

412
00:23:44,717 --> 00:23:47,217
TODAY WE TAKE THE FIGHT
TO THEM.

413
00:23:47,250 --> 00:23:51,850
WE SHALL DESTROY THE DEMONS
AND BRING PEACE TO OUR WORLD
FOREVERMORE!

414
00:23:55,217 --> 00:23:57,817
YUKIO OKUMURA.

415
00:24:03,217 --> 00:24:05,983
[ SHIEMI ]
HEY, RIN, IS THIS REALLY
WHAT AN EXORCIST'S JOB IS?

416
00:24:06,017 --> 00:24:07,950
I DON'T FEEL RIGHT ABOUT THIS.

417
00:24:07,983 --> 00:24:10,183
[ RIN ]
ARE YOU OUT OF YOUR MIND?

418
00:24:10,217 --> 00:24:13,417
[ YUKIO ]
YOU'D BETTER LET GO OF ME, RIN.
I SAID LET GO OF ME!

